wonderful /ˈwʌndəfʊl/

1. ADJ If you describe something or someone as wonderful , you think they are extremely good. 极好的 

例： The cold, misty air felt wonderful on his face. 那凉凉的雾气使他脸上感觉好极了。 

例： It's wonderful to see you. 见到你好极了。 

2. wonderfully ADV 极好地 

例： It's a system that works wonderfully well. 它是一个运行极好的系统。

